title: Chicago 24 (XXIV) -- Heart of Chicago Volume 2 + bonus track
description:
Here it is, the second one in the two-volume Heart of Chicago set.  Enjoy


Included in this album:



Dialogue (Parts 1 & II)

Old Days

All Roads Lead to You

Love Me Tomorrow

Baby What A Big Surprise

You&#039;re Not Alone

What Kind of Man Would I Be?

No Tell Lover

Show Me a Sign

(I&#039;ve Been) Searchin&#039; So Long

Call on Me

I Don&#039;t Wanna Live Without Your Love

Feelin&#039; Stronger Every Day

Stay the Night

I&#039;m a Man

25 or 6 to 4


Plus the bonus track found on the "We Are the World" album from 1984 to benefit starving people in Africa.  Since there are no more starving people in Africa it obviously did its job.

Good For Nothing


CHICAGO BELONGS IN THE HALL OF FAME!
